<paragraph blockId="21.[264,1324,1399,1905]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
Coloration as described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Rao" box="[587,947,1399,1425]" pageId="21" pageNumber="48" refString="Rao, K. R. &amp; Emiliyamma, K. G. (1995) On two new species of Scaphoideus Uhler (Homoptera: Cicadellidae) from Madumalai, Tamil Nadu. Hexapoda, 7, 79 - 84." type="journal article" year="1995">
Rao and Emiliayamma (
<number box="[874,938,1399,1425]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="1995.0">1995</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
. Head narrower than pronotum, angularly produced. Vertex as long as inter­ocular width, shorter than pronotum.
</paragraph>
